    "title": "Pumziko la sabato ya Mungu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "pumziko la sabato ya mungu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Wazo la pumziko la sabato la Mungu (kama ilivyoelezwa katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:1-Heb4:11\">Waebrania 4:1–11</a>) limekuwa gumu kwa wasomi wengi kuelewa. Linajumuisha mawazo kutoka kwenye Agano la Kale, kama vile Nchi ya Ahadi kama mahali pa kupumzika kutoka utumwani na kutangatanga. Pia linazungumzia siku ya sabato kama siku ya kupumzika ya kila wiki. Katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:19\">Waebrania 3:7–19</a>, mwandishi anarejelea <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:7-Ps95:11\">Zaburi 95:7–11</a>. Anatumia mfano wa Waisraeli waliotangatanga nyikani kama mfano wa wale ambao hawakuingia katika pumziko la Mungu kwa sababu hawakutii.</p><p>Je, ni &quot;pumziko&quot; gani ambalo hawakuweza kuingia, ambalo bado linabaki kwa watu wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:1-Heb4:3\">Waebrania 4:1–3</a>)? Mwandishi wa Waebrania alimaanisha zaidi ya ardhi ya kimwili ya Kanaani kama mahali pa &quot;pumziko la sabato&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:8-Heb4:9\">4:8–9</a>). <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:2\">Mwanzo 2:2</a> inaelezea pumziko la Mungu kama kitu kilichoandaliwa &quot;tangu msingi wa ulimwengu&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:3-Heb4:4\">Waebrania 4:3–4</a>). Pumziko la Mungu linahusisha kusitisha kazi ya mtu mwenyewe, kama Mungu alivyofanya (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:10\">4:10</a>). Wale wanaosikia &quot;sauti Yake,&quot; hawafanyi mioyo yao kuwa migumu, na wanaamini habari njema kuhusu Yesu wanaweza &quot;kuingia katika pumziko hilo&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:1-Heb4:3\">4:1–3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:7\">7</a>).</p><p>Agano la Kale linaita Siku ya Upatanisho “siku ya sabato ya pumziko kamili” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:29-Lev16:31\">Mambo ya Walawi 16:29–31</a>). Katika siku hiyo, watu walikomesha kazi zao zote. Katika Agano Jipya, Yesu, Kuhani wetu Mkuu, alitoa dhabihu ya mara moja ambayo ilifanya &quot;kuondoa dhambi&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:7-Heb9:28\">9:7–28</a>). Alikuwa dhabihu ya mwisho ya upatanisho, akileta amani kati ya Mungu na watu. Yesu anawapa watu pumziko la kiroho. Wanaweza kuingia katika pumziko hili kwa kuamini na kutii habari njema hii.</p><p>Pumziko la Mungu kupitia Yesu lina vipengele viwili:</p><ol><li><p>Wale wanaomfuata Yesu wanaacha kujaribu kupata kukubalika kwa Mungu kupitia juhudi zao wenyewe. Wanamwamini kazi iliyokamilika ya Yesu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">Waefeso 2:8–9</a>). Wanapata amani na Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">Yohana 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36\">Matendo 10:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">Warumi 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:19-2Cor5:21\">2 Wakorintho 5:19–21</a>).</p></li><li><p>Wanatarajia pumziko la milele na furaha katika uwepo wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">Isaya 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:13\">Ufunuo 14:13</a>). Yesu Kristo anatoa pumziko kamili na bora (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">Mathayo 11:28–30</a>).</p></li></ol><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:1-Gen2:3\">Mwanzo 2:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:21-Exod16:29\">Kutoka 16:21–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:8-Exod20:11\">20:8–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:13-Exod31:16\">31:13–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:29-Lev16:31\">Mambo ya Walawi 16:29–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">Isaya 52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:13-Isa54:14\">54:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:2\">56:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:4\">4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:2\">57:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:21\">21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:13\">58:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:20\">Ezekieli 20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">Mathayo 11:28–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:23-Mark2:28\">Marko 2:23–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:48\">Luka 8:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">Yohana 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36\">Matendo 10:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">Warumi 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:19-2Cor5:21\">2 Wakorintho 5:19–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:17\">Waefeso 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:20\">Wakolosai 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:16\">2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:1-Heb4:11\">Waebrania 4:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:2\">2 Petro 1:2</a></p>",
